Project: Project Exchange
Architecture: Clearing & Settlement Split
Core Logic:
- Project Exchange Core: Order-matching and virtual accounting.
- Accounting Ledger: Double-entry system for operator debts.
- Settlement Gateway: External payment instructions.
- Wallet Proxy: B2C third-party wallet integration.

